### File 2: `pkg/image/cache.go`

Import the controller metrics package and increment the counter on cache hit.

**Changes:**

Add import (aliased to avoid conflict with the existing `pkg/image/metrics` import):

```go
ctrlmetrics "github.com/openshift/multiarch-tuning-operator/internal/controller/podplacement/metrics"
```

In `GetCompatibleArchitecturesSet`, inside the cache-hit branch (after line 52 `if architectures, ok := ...`), add:

```go
if ctrlmetrics.ImageCacheHits != nil {
    ctrlmetrics.ImageCacheHits.With(prometheus.Labels{"image_ref": imageReference}).Inc()
}
```

The nil guard is necessary because `ImageCacheHits` is only initialized when `InitPodPlacementControllerMetrics()` is called (which only happens in controller mode, not in tests or other contexts).

